<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">value</ENAMEX> added by design review processes is not well
established.


Although research has been done by the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Construction Industry</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Institute</ENAMEX> and other <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">organizations</ENAMEX> to identify metrics that may be
