construction means and methods and delivery of the completed
facility within the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">owner</ENAMEX>'s scope of work for cost, time, and
quality.
Under this approach, the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">owner</ENAMEX> typically retains responsibility
