defines the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">owner</ENAMEX>'s expectations regarding <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">facility</ENAMEX> cost, schedule,
performance, and quality. The <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">owner</ENAMEX>'s standards, more than those of
